<p><strong>Ian Maurer</strong></p>
<p>ECE, Georgia Tech</p>
<p>Ph.D student 2025-</p>
<p>B.S. University of Georgia</p>
<p><strong>Bio:</strong></p>
<p>Ian Maurer is a PhD student in Electrical Engineering at Georgia Tech. He graduated from the University of Georgia with a Bachelor’s degree in Electrical Engineering in 2021.  He is investigating recent trends related to distributed energy resources, especially rooftop solar panels, and their impacts on power system resilience.</p>
